product_description: Know Productivity - Efficiency - Passion - Creativity with no limits. A crisp IPS display boasts everything from pomodoro timer, to a playful Tamagotchi-style companion, a trusty clock and much more.

Build your muscle memory faster, with all your shortcuts in one place.

Map pretty much anything to the dials/keys for easy access to things like font size, shapes, send to back/front, zoom, and much more…

high grade build
